          "publishedAt": "2026-06-07T08:40:25.000Z",
          "author": "Michal Sutter",
          "summary": "<p>Low-code and no-code AI platforms now turn a prompt into a working app, agent, or model. This guide compares 21 tools across app builders, automation, AI agents, and machine learning platforms, each linked to its official site.</p> <p>The post <a href=\"https://www.marktechpost.com/2026/06/07/best-21-low-code-and-no-code-ai-tools-in-2026/\">Best 21 Low-Code and No-Code AI Tools in 2026</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.marktechpost.com\">MarkTechPost</a>.</p>",
